# SDA Church App Git Configuration
# Aligned with Tenet 5 (Simplicity) via a Whitelist-first approach.
# This mirrors the logic of .aiexclude to ensure absolute consistency.

# 1. Ignore everything by default
/*

# 2. Re-include source and configuration directories
!/.github/
!/app/
!/assets/
!/components/
!/constants/
!/docs/
!/public/
!/services/
!/styles/

# 3. Re-include root configuration files
!/*.json
!/*.md
!/*.js
!/*.ts
!/*.tsx
!/*.html
!/.gitignore
!/.aiexclude
!/.env.example
!/.vscode

# 4. Explicitly ignore generated or sensitive noise
# These are excluded even if they match whitelisted patterns.
node_modules/
.expo/
dist/
web-build/
expo-env.d.ts
*.tsbuildinfo
.env*
